    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven achieved levels below the required level 4 threshold for MRL 5. Six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. The hemodynamic boundary-condition dataset (dataVintage 2018-03-15) was used without re-validation following the model revision of 2026-01-10. Despite these gaps, the package is recorded as Accepted for system-testing purposes to exercise weakener-detection logic for W-EP-03.",
